  <brief_title>Blood Pressure Reactivity After Resistance Exercise in Older Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>BLOOD PRESSURE REACTIVITY TO MENTAL STRESS IS ATTENUATED FOLLOWING RESISTANCE EXERCISE IN ELDERLY HYPERTENSIVE WOMEN</official_title>
